name: Jelly Dash
description:
Try to climb walls without hitting obstacles in your path. Collect coins and choose from different jelly characters.

Make your way to the top and jump across walls in Jelly Dash. Avoid any obstacles and beat your high score. Get more characters to multiply your score.

Download link: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.moonwire.jellydash
